I"÷<p>Adjust Brightness/Contrast values.</p>

<h3 id="brightness"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Brightness</code></h3>

<p>Move the joystick up or down to adjust the luminance of the backlight from 0 to 100.</p>

<h3 id="contrast"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Contrast</code></h3>

<p>Adjust brightness first, and then adjust contrast only if further adjustment is desired. Move the joystick up or down to adjust between darkness and lightness from 0 to 100.</p>
